{"tid":2083606,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「方向報反了！」躁男與妻爭吵險釀群毆 警犬震懾拘16人檢刀錘","createTime":"2020-06-29T00:53:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T02:25:32.000Z","uid":71166,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4228c632f40342b0e755b5bba1b1d4d6f2f580e6","tid":2083606,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T00:53:52.000Z","msg":"旺角渡船街與豉油街交界一酒店對開，昨晚(27日)11時許，一名男子在酒店內，因故與妻子爭吵，消息稱，有人疑氣憤下召來一批大漢助威，聚集近20人，一時間人聲嘈雜，氣氛緊張。聚集人群驚動附近途人報案求助。<br />\n<br />\n其後，大批機動部隊及衝鋒隊警員趕至，發現酒店外聚集大批人士，部分人有紋身，兇神惡煞，其中6人更逃進酒店內躲避，警員隨即在酒店大堂及門外，將在場各人截停查問，並帶同警犬震懾場面。同時，警員發現酒店內一名身穿黑衣男子，在一輛平治房車旁神情慌張，亦上前查看，並於車尾箱搜出11把刀及兩柄鐵錘，懷疑在場有兩批人士準備群毆。<br />\n<br />\n警方經初步調查後，以涉嫌「非法集結」拘捕懷疑涉案的16名男子，年齡介乎29至50歲，而持有平治房車車匙的姓李(46歲)男子，亦涉「藏有攻擊性武器」被捕。警員將被捕16人逐一鎖上手銬帶返警署扣查，案件交由旺角警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/kkE.N.9RUl4fO_73oKIX1A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-06/43db8860-b8df-11ea-bd7b-fc0f3243ce60\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FkkE.N.9RUl4fO_73oKIX1A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-06%2F43db8860-b8df-11ea-bd7b-fc0f3243ce60&h=fc86e5bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>警犬震懾拘16人檢刀錘</ins></strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0efc7397848489de2d1554bf662538373aa1fb11","tid":2083606,"uid":304032,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T00:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mbo5fOT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMbo5fOT.jpg&h=c2170d9d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YmYXRne.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYmYXRne.jpg&h=47d8c4